My keyboard is experiencing dificulties with the letter 'i'. It
sometimes types it infinitely or it refuses to type it at all. I think
its fixed, but just warnin' ya guys.

::Incarcinator::

They must be getting pretty desperate to try to kamakazee shuttles
into me, Incarcinator thinks to himself as he dodges the next few
shots after nearly being hit by a transport ship, since he was
prepared for them. One of them hits him in the leg, flipping him a
bit.
